<li>The <a href="/wiki/Netherlands" title="Netherlands">Netherlands</a> (sole official language in every province except <a href="/wiki/Friesland" title="Friesland">Friesland</a>, where <a href="/wiki/West_Frisian" title="West Frisian">West Frisian</a> is co-official)
