</ul>
<p><b><a href="/wiki/Moldovan_language" title="Moldovan language">Moldovan</a></b> (identical to <a href="#Romanian" title="">Romanian</a> according to the law of Moldova<sup id="cite_ref-moldovan_3-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-moldovan-3" title=""><span>[</span>4<span>]</span></a></sup>)</p>
