<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Mongolia" title="Mongolia">Mongolia</a></li>
<li>part of the <a href="/wiki/People%27s_Republic_of_China" title="People's Republic of China">People's Republic of China</a>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Inner_Mongolia" title="Inner Mongolia">Inner Mongolia</a>, with Chinese (Mandarin)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Haixi_Mongol_and_Tibetan_Autonomous_Prefecture" title="Haixi Mongol and Tibetan Autonomous Prefecture">Haixi</a>, with Tibetan and Chinese (Mandarin)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Bortala_Mongol_Autonomous_Prefecture" title="Bortala Mongol Autonomous Prefecture">Bortala</a>, with Chinese (Mandarin)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Bayin%27gholin_Mongol_Autonomous_Prefecture" title="Bayin'gholin Mongol Autonomous Prefecture" class="mw-redirect">Bayin'gholin</a>, with Chinese (Mandarin)</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Dorbod_Autonomous_County&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Dorbod Autonomous County (page does not exist)">Dorbod</a>, with Chinese (Mandarin)</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Qian_Gorlos_Mongol_Autonomous_County&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Qian Gorlos Mongol Autonomous County (page does not exist)">Qian Gorlos</a>, with Chinese (Mandarin)</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Harqin_Left_Mongol_Autonomous_County&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Harqin Left Mongol Autonomous County (page does not exist)">Harqin Left</a>, with Chinese (Mandarin)</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Fuxin_Mongol_Autonomous_County&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Fuxin Mongol Autonomous County (page does not exist)">Fuxin</a>, with Chinese (Mandarin)</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Weichang_Manchu_and_Mongol_Autonomous_County&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Weichang Manchu and Mongol Autonomous County (page does not exist)">Weichang</a>, with Chinese (Mandarin)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Subei_Mongol_Autonomous_County" title="Subei Mongol Autonomous County">Subei</a>, with Chinese (Mandarin)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Henan_Mongol_Autonomous_County" title="Henan Mongol Autonomous County">Henan</a>, with Chinese (Mandarin)</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
