<li><a href="/wiki/Romania" title="Romania">Romania</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Moldova" title="Moldova">Moldova</a> (official called <a href="#Moldovan" title="">Moldovan</a>, although identical to Romanian according to the law of Moldova<sup id="cite_ref-moldovan_3-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-moldovan-3" title=""><span>[</span>4<span>]</span></a></sup>)</li>
<li>part of <a href="/wiki/Serbia" title="Serbia">Serbia</a>
<ul>
