</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Singapore" title="Singapore">Singapore</a> (with English, <a href="/wiki/Chinese_language" title="Chinese language">Chinese</a> and Malay)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Sri_Lanka" title="Sri Lanka">Sri Lanka</a> (with Sinhala, and with English as a link language)</li>
</ul>
<p><b><a href="/wiki/Telugu_language" title="Telugu language">Telugu</a></b>:</p>
<ul>
