<p><a name="Official_languages_of_subnational_entities" id="Official_languages_of_subnational_entities"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=List_of_official_languages&amp;action=edit&amp;section=35" title="Edit section: Official languages of subnational entities">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Official languages of subnational entities</span></h2>
<div class="notice plainlinks"><i>This list is <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:WikiProject_Lists#Incomplete_lists" title="Wikipedia:WikiProject Lists">incomplete</a>; you can help by <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=List_of_official_languages&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=List_of_official_languages&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow">expanding it</a></i>.</div>
<p><b>Aranese</b> <i>see <b>Occitan</b></i></p>
<p><b><a href="/wiki/Armenian_language" title="Armenian language">Armenian</a>:</b></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Nagorno_Karabagh" title="Nagorno Karabagh" class="mw-redirect">Nagorno Karabagh</a></li>
