</ul>
<p><b><a href="/wiki/Standard_Cantonese" title="Standard Cantonese">Cantonese Chinese</a></b>:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Hong_Kong" title="Hong Kong">Hong Kong</a> (for <a href="/wiki/Chinese_language" title="Chinese language">Chinese language</a>, both Cantonese and <a href="/wiki/Standard_Mandarin" title="Standard Mandarin">Mandarin</a> are spoken <i>de facto</i>; co-official with English)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Macau" title="Macau">Macau</a> (for Chinese language, both Cantonese and Mandarin are spoken <i>de facto</i>; co-official with Portuguese)</li>
</ul>
<p><b><a href="/wiki/Catalan_language" title="Catalan language">Catalan</a></b>:</p>
<ul>
